foods.description: COUNTRY SAUSAGE & BISCUITS WITH CHEESE, CHEESE
foods.lowercaseDescription: country sausage & biscuits with cheese, cheese
foods.ingredients: BISCUIT INGREDIENTS: UNBLEACHED ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR [FLOUR, BARLEY MALT, NIACIN (VITAMIN B3), IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE (VITAMIN B1), RIBOFLAVIN (VITAMIN B2), FOLIC ACID (VITAMIN B9)], WATER, SUGAR, SOYBEAN OIL, YEAST, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: POTATO FLOUR, SALT, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (TO RETAIN FRESHNESS), WHEY, YEAST NUTRIENTS (MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE), DOUGH CONDITIONERS (MONOGLYCERIDES). SAUSAGE INGREDIENTS: PORK (INCLUDING THE HAM, LOIN, AND TENDERLOIN), WATER, SALT, CORN SYRUP SOLIDS, SPICES, SODIUM PHOSPHATES, SUGAR, MONOSODIUM GLUTAMATE, AND CARAMEL COLORING. CHEESE INGREDIENTS: AMERICAN CHEESE (CULTURED MILK, SALT, ENZYMES, ANNATTO COLOR), WATER, CREAM, SODIUM CITRATE, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF SALT, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, CITRIC ACID, ACETIC ACID, SORBIC ACID (PRESERVATIVE), SOY LECITHIN, APOCAROTENAL AND BETA CAROTENE (COLOR)
